{"tid":540038,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Google：台灣人愛玩手機遊戲 亞洲排第二","createTime":"2018-01-25T06:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T16:15:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fde64bd8d5627f1316699809eb98401c5ca5246b","tid":540038,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Google Play亞太區總經理James Sanders昨（24）日指出，目前台灣在行動市場中仍位居全球領先地位，也是Google Play全球的前5大市場之一，且台灣用戶喜歡玩手機遊戲，在亞太國家中排名第二，甚至超過日本、南韓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3072/e3072019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3072%2Fe3072019.jpg&h=23a1fc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180124004984-260412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180124004984-260412&d=0o5azslwCYS4FXC%2BZHkPgrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=646980eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180124004984-260412</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180124/1099339.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180124%2F1099339.htm&d=0o5azslwCYS4FXC%2BZHkPgrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=b39ed0f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180124/1099339.htm</a></div>"},{"pid":"028d386cf47ebff3943144bc79f4888d566a4511","tid":540038,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"截至 2017 年 5 月在超過 190 個國家擁有超過 10 億的活躍用戶，過去一年累積超過 820 億下載次數，截至 2017 年 10 月的調查，全球用戶在 Google Play 每月有 80 億的新下載次數，在這當中，台灣仍為 Google Play 的前五大市場。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3072/e3072054.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3072%2Fe3072054.jpg&h=e548b8b5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 亞太區總經理 James Sanders 稍早說明 Google Play 在 2017 年的發展，在這當中消費者使用智慧型手機的活躍度已經從 2013 年有 46% 透過智慧型手機上網，到了 2017 年已經成長到驚人的 92%，每個人平均擁有 2.7 個連網裝置，而在台灣每週至少玩一次手機遊戲的用戶比率高達 33%，在亞太地區僅次於越南（36%）的國家，即使是遊戲強國南韓也僅有 24%。"},{"pid":"88343ae475ddd2c91a609d98efa112295178f7d7","tid":540038,"uid":18568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"手機驚最垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf6ecb9d682a11646679951a93a6688a831c3a8","tid":540038,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"會有這樣的龐大幅度成長，James 認為，智慧型手機是一個相對於 PC、電視平台來說相對容易使用的平台，在家裡你可能會用電視看電影，但是你在移動的時候，透過智慧型手機會更加方便。而且透過 Android 系統不斷的更新，現在的智慧型手機體驗已經越來越好。第三是使用體驗，如果是在 5 年前，Google Play 當中有相當多的應用程式，但多數都是遊戲被看到，但是透過不斷的改良，遊戲品質不但更加提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而且透過現在的分類方式，消費者可以在 Google Play快速找到他們喜歡的應用程式。"},{"pid":"8a7d9740441be599bb51de2df7a1f4d82a8f86e9","tid":540038,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"越南竟然第一<br />\n日本竟然第四"},{"pid":"5dfeacae0e479aa31adcf5edb4fbfbd1e80790b2","tid":540038,"uid":119778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁弱智"},{"pid":"a3ab023167c056841f9a0ac86a2d3402e9050bda","tid":540038,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782f986d92b167ab6049ddad1fd685cbc2b0ad75","tid":540038,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"都唔明點解有人會玩手機game<br />\n一味課金抽蛋，抽極都係比垃圾你，引你繼續抽"}]}